{"tid":1036040,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《還願》最尾結局既手法鋪排都算世界級，男人老狗都喊撚左～","createTime":"2019-02-25T03:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T15:48:59.000Z","uid":49388,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"582dc2c325e0622204af65e364e118686947f9f0","tid":1036040,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"開廁所門美心獨白 <br />\n<br />\n&gt;<br />\n<br />\n起歌《還願》<br />\n<br />\n&gt;<br />\n<br />\n美心：爸爸，我們回家吧～ <span style=\"color: red;\">（個囡到最尾都無怪爸爸，而爸爸為左個囡勾利都濟，證明佢真係好鍚個囡，去到呢個位個心已經痛到痴撚線）</span>  <br />\n<br />\n&gt; <br />\n<br />\n再到個囡唱《碼頭姑娘》<span style=\"color: red;\">（真係第一次聽到細路唱歌咁有感情）</span> <br />\n<br />\n&gt; <br />\n<br />\n若有來世，你<span style=\"color: red;\">還願</span>意嗎？<span style=\"color: red;\">（國語孩願，還願，你還願意當我的爸爸嗎？）</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&gt;<br />\n<br />\n老母入房唔敲門見到我喊 <span style=\"color: red;\">(屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span>"},{"pid":"1fdd8f432741b595a705d6018e59d80ea6ddcee4","tid":1036040,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb165ff74ff3e852588495aa27136c285eb77079","tid":1036040,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"D人話比分果度不停88=女兒紅個時拍門叫爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e0af8d2de1aaa7beab08a454b3e03a2273050b","tid":1036040,"uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"好難抽離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7289a877ede5ab38b314e23e2c242304d1c7dc","tid":1036040,"uid"